headline: Will Palantir Stock Trounce Nvidia in the Second Half of 2025?
summary: Palantir Technologies' stock has handily outperformed Nvidia so far this year.  Palantir should continue to enjoy commercial momentum, while the Trump administration's trade policies weigh on Nvidia.  If Palantir Technologies (NASDAQ: PLTR) and Nvidia (NASDAQ: NVDA) were in the stock equivalent of a boxing match, we'd have a technical knockout so far this year.

headline: This Company Signed an AI Deal With Palantir. Could It Be the Next Big Growth Stock?
summary: Palantir in March announced an artificial intelligence (AI) partnership with Archer Aviation.  Archer isn't generating revenue, but it has big plans for growth in the air taxi industry.  Palantir Technologies (NASDAQ: PLTR) has been one of the top artificial intelligence (AI) stocks to own in recent years.
